    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "FIJI AIRWAYS\nAIRCRAFT\nMODEL\nAIRBUS A330-200\nSCALE: 1:200\nAIRWAYS",
      "SAIGALE 1800-200\nFIJI AIRWAYS IS THE PROUD NATIONAL AIRLINE OF FIJI. THE AIRLINE'S LIVERY\nFEATURES A DISTINCTIVE FIJIAN MASI ARTWORK DESIGNED BY RENOWNED FIJIAN\nMASI ARTIST MAKERETA MATEMOSI. HERE IS A DESCRIPTION OF THE MASI MOTIFS\nTHAT FEATURE ON OUR AIRCRAFT AND THEIR MEANINGS.\nTETEVA\nInterconnection, friendly\nnature and our love for Fiji.\nMAKARE\nClear water flowing on\na white sandy beach.\nROVA\nExtends a warm welcome\nto our visitors",
